      "contents": [
        {
          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, I hear you. What you're describing goes beyond running, and it matters.\n\nWhen someone says they don't want to be here anymore, I take that seriously. Please reach out for support right now.\n\n**988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline:** Call or text 988 (US, available 24/7)\n**Crisis Text Line:** Text HOME to 741741\n\nYou don't have to work through this alone. Please contact one of those resources now.\n\nI'm here when you're ready to talk running again."
        }
      ],
